@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xhgssy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos(v0) * v2)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs((tmp + 0.90 + v1 + 0.94)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v0 + 0.90 + v0 + 0.19)))
    v0 = ((v1 / wp.exp(v1 + 0.00)) * 0.57)
    v1 = v0
    v1 = 0.68
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
